## ERB in Fixtures

```yaml
# test/fixtures/articles.yml

recent:
  title: Recent Article
  body: Body text
  created_at: <%= 1.day.ago %>
  updated_at: <%= 1.day.ago %>

old:
  title: Old Article
  body: Body text
  created_at: <%= 1.year.ago %>
  updated_at: <%= 1.year.ago %>

# Using loops
<% 10.times do |i| %>
article_<%= i %>:
  title: Article <%= i %>
  body: Body <%= i %>
  created_at: <%= i.days.ago %>
<% end %>
```

